      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
